doctype html
html
  head
    title Weather Blog - About Us
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='style.css')
    script(src='https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js')
  body
    nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-dark
      .container
        .navbar-brand
          a.logo(href='/') Weather Forecast
        button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarNav', aria-controls='navbarNav', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
          span.navbar-toggler-icon
        .collapse.navbar-collapse#navbarNav
          ul.navbar-nav.ml-auto
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='/') Home
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='/Forecast') Forecast
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='/Articles') Articles
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='/AboutUs') About Us
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='/contact') Contact
          .search-box.navbar-nav
            form.form-inline.my-2.my-lg-0
              input.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Search')
              button.btn.btn-outline-light(type='submit')
                i.fa.fa-search

    main.container.content
      .container.mt-5
        .row
          .col-md-8.mx-auto
            .card.box-shadow
              .card-body
                h5.card-title About Us
                p.card-text
                  | Welcome to Weather Blog! We are a passionate team of weather enthusiasts who are dedicated to providing you with accurate and up-to-date weather information from around the world.
                  | Our mission is to make weather data accessible to everyone in a user-friendly and informative way.
                p.card-text
                  | With years of experience in meteorology and data analysis, we ensure that our weather forecasts are reliable and trustworthy. We strive to keep you informed about weather patterns, forecasts, and climatic trends.
                  | Whether you're planning a vacation, a weekend getaway, or simply curious about the weather in your area, we've got you covered.
                p.card-text
                  | We believe that understanding the weather is crucial for making informed decisions and staying safe. Our team is committed to providing you with insights into the science behind weather phenomena, so you can better comprehend the world around you.
                  | Thank you for choosing Weather Blog as your go-to source for weather information. Feel free to explore our articles, forecasts, and resources to enhance your knowledge of the weather.
                p.card-text
                  | If you have any questions, feedback, or suggestions, don't hesitate to get in touch with us. We value your input and are constantly striving to improve our services to meet your weather-related needs.
                  | Stay informed, stay curious, and stay weather-wise with Weather Blog!
